  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_interface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=479\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_interface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"682\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637058\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_interface.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bf5b7892-b042-4e97-8999-1187fb7d0510\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_interface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=958 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_interface.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=479 1x\"></span><hr/><h3 id=\"GettingStartedinBlender-LoadingtheAddon\">Loading the Addon</h3><p>Like any other addon for Blender, RenderMan for Blender can be loaded/enabled from the Preferences (Edit→Preferences), under the Addons tab. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=417\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"593\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637061\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_prefs_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9d6cacd0-e515-408b-a7c6-d2a0a720e010\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=834 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685453&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=417 1x\"></span><p><br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"GettingStartedinBlender-FindingRenderManProServer\">Finding RenderMan Pro Server</h3><p>As mentioned in the <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFB27/pages/544636971/Installation+of+RenderMan+for+Blender\" rel=\"nofollow\">installation</a> docs, RenderMan for Blender requires RenderMan Pro Server (RPS) to be installed on your machine. How the addon finds RPS can be set in the preferences:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/prferences_find_rmantree.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=658&amp;height=544\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/prferences_find_rmantree.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"544\" data-width=\"658\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637040\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"prferences_find_rmantree.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7a2b3290-e610-4b5d-83da-cb3db56777df\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/prferences_find_rmantree.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=658&amp;height=544 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/prferences_find_rmantree.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685029&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=658&amp;height=544 1x\"></span><p>Changing <strong>RenderMan Location</strong> to <strong>Choose From Installed</strong> will allow you to select from the ones that are installed in the default location. You can also set it to <strong>Set Manually</strong> and manually set the location of RPS. The default is to consult the <strong>RMANTREE</strong> environment variable. Any changes to this will require a restart of Blender.</p><p>The addon will try a couple of different fallbacks if one of the methods fails. Here's the order of operations:</p><ul><li><p>First, try and find based on your preference.</p></li><li><p>If the choice from installed or set manually has failed, we fallback on consulting the <strong>RMANTREE</strong> environment variable</p></li><li><p>If the preference was to consult <strong>RMANTREE </strong>and that failed, we fallback to try and detect the latest version found in the default installation path</p></li></ul><p /><hr/><p /><h3 id=\"GettingStartedinBlender-YourFirstRender\">Your First Render</h3><p>To start rendering with RenderMan, change the current Render Engine setting to RenderMan Render.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>To do that you can either:</strong></p><p>1. Use the handy Use RenderMan shortcut in the object context menu. Right-click in the viewport and select Use RenderMan.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=519\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"739\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637064\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_prefs_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2cd90abf-8b23-4900-815a-8f5c2978f270\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1400&amp;height=808 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685624&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=519 1x\"></span><p /><p>2. Or change it from the render properties panel</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=389\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"415\" data-width=\"959\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637067\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_prefs_2a.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3066626b-db58-4fa8-b730-02d1ec454312\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=959&amp;height=415 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_2a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=389 1x\"></span><p /><hr/><p /><p>To render, you can click on the Render button in the render properties panel, or use the Render shortcut from the object context menu in the viewport:</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=733\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"781\" data-width=\"958\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_prefs_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a92a8a37-4637-4227-a951-2b84f545166b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=958&amp;height=781 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685625&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=733 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=470\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"669\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637073\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_prefs_3a.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637021\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"747bd715-bb7a-415a-b20b-f487e6b22765\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1500&amp;height=784 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544637021/RenderManForBlender_prefs_3a.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432685801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=470 1x\"></span><p /><p>Your render should appear in the Blender render window.</p><p>Alternatively, you can also render to RenderMan's &quot;<a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661909\" rel=\"nofollow\">it</a>&quot; framebuffer by changing the <strong>Render To</strong> setting from &quot;Blender&quot; to &quot;it&quot;.</p><p /><p /><p />"
    }
  },
